OL,3,CGerry Adams 'peacemaker reputation
OL,4,Cdamaged by BBC' claim
OL,6,FGerry Adams' reputation as a
OL,7,F"peacemaker" suffered an "unjustified"
OL,8,Fattack when the BBC broadcast an
OL,9,Fallegation that he had sanctioned the
OL,10,Fmurder of an informer, a civil case
OL,11,Fhas been told.
OL,13,FBarrister for Mr Adams, Tom Hogan SC,
OL,14,Faccused the BBC of "reckless" and
OL,15,F"arrogant" behaviour, and believing it
OL,16,Fcould say anything about Mr Adams.
