OL,6,FThe former Sinn Fein president entered
OL,7,Fthe witness box at the end of the
OL,8,Ffirst day of the defamation case in
OL,9,FDublin High Court, where he described
OL,10,Fhis early political awakenings in
OL,11,FBelfast in the 1960s.
OL,13,FThe ex-MP launched the case after
OL,14,Fclaims were made in a BBC Northern
OL,15,FIreland Spotlight programme in 2016
OL,16,Fover who sanctioned the killing of
OL,17,FBritish spy Denis Donaldson.
