OL,3,CGerry Adams 'peacemaker reputation
OL,4,Cdamaged by BBC' claim
OL,6,FSinn Fein member Mr Donaldson, 55, was
OL,7,Fshot dead at a cottage near Glenties
OL,8,Fin Co Donegal in April 2006 after
OL,9,Fbeing exposed as an informer.
OL,11,FMr Adams has denied the allegation
OL,12,Fthat he had any involvement in
OL,13,Fordering the murder.
OL,15,FMaking his opening statement to the
OL,16,Fjury, Mr Hogan said Mr Adams needed no
OL,17,Fintroduction.
OL,19,FHe said: "He is credited, with others,
OL,20,Fin bringing about the peace process in
OL,21,FNorthern Ireland."
