OL,4,Cdamaged by BBC' claim
OL,6,FThe barrister added: "Gerry Adams'
OL,7,Freputation is that of a peacemaker.
OL,9,F"It has taken Gerry Adams a lifetime
OL,10,Fto gain that reputation.
OL,12,F"The essence of this case is an
OL,13,Funjustified attack on his reputation."
OL,15,FThe barrister told the jury that Mr
OL,16,FAdams had been meeting Tony Blair in
OL,17,FLondon when Mr Donaldson, who had
OL,18,Fadmitted being a British agent, was
OL,19,Fkilled in 2006.
