OL,6,FHe said the Provisional IRA had said
OL,7,Fit was not involved in the murder and
OL,8,Fthat it had later been claimed by the
OL,9,FReal IRA.
OL,11,FHe said years later in 2016, Mr Adams
OL,12,Fhad received a letter "out of the
OL,13,Fblue" from BBC Spotlight journalist
OL,14,FJennifer O'Leary.
OL,16,FMr Adams had been asked to respond to
OL,17,Fallegations that he had the "final
OL,18,Fsay" on sanctions taken by the IRA
OL,19,Fagainst Mr Donaldson.
