OL,6,FFollowing a second letter, Mr Adams
OL,7,Fresponded to the BBC that he had no
OL,8,Fknowledge or involvement in the murder.
OL,10,FThe court heard the BBC Spotlight
OL,11,Fprogramme was broadcast in September
OL,12,F2016.
OL,14,FMr Hogan said it contained a claim
OL,15,Ffrom an anonymous source, who said
OL,16,Fthey were an informer within the IRA,
OL,17,Fthat Mr Adams had the final say in the
OL,18,Fkilling of Mr Donaldson.
