OL,6,FThe barrister said the same allegation
OL,7,Fwas made in a story on the BBC website
OL,8,Fthe following day.
OL,10,FMr Hogan said the allegation that Mr
OL,11,FAdams had sanctioned the murder was
OL,12,F"not true".
OL,14,FHe said the BBC would not be standing
OL,15,Fover the allegation that the former
OL,16,FSinn Fein president sanctioned the
OL,17,Fmurder of Mr Donaldson during the
OL,18,Fongoing case.
