OL,6,FThe barrister said it was a
OL,7,F"journalistic no-no" for the BBC to
OL,8,Fbroadcast serious allegations about Mr
OL,9,FAdams relying on a single anonymous
OL,10,Fsource.
OL,12,FHe said: "It was never put to the
OL,13,Fanonymous source that Gerry Adams
OL,14,Fdenied involvement.
OL,16,F"We say the BBC did not undertake the
OL,17,Flevel of verification required or
OL,18,Findeed any verification."
