OL,6,FHe added: "This programme should have
OL,7,Fcome with a serious health warning
OL,8,Fthat the allegation was unverified.
OL,10,F"It was reckless journalism."
OL,12,FHe said: "Many people say many things
OL,13,Fabout Gerry Adams and he may have sued
OL,14,Fbefore, but over time he has let
OL,15,Fmatters go, usually on legal advice.
OL,17,F"But he wasn't willing to let this
OL,18,Fmatter pass."
