OL,7,Ffrom the BBC that it could "say
OL,8,Fanything about Gerry Adams", including
OL,9,Fcalling him a murderer.
OL,11,FThe barrister said Mr Adams was a
OL,12,F"polarising character".
OL,14,FHe added: "To some he is a hero, to
OL,15,Fsome he is not."
