OL,6,FMr Adams was then called as the first
OL,7,Fwitness.He told the court about his
OL,8,Fearly upbringing in Belfast, his
OL,9,Finvolvement in the civil rights
OL,10,Fmovement and the beginning of the
OL,11,FTroubles in Northern Ireland in the
OL,12,F1960s.
OL,14,FEarlier in the day judge Mr Justice
OL,15,FAlexander Owens said the trial is
OL,16,Flikely to last four weeks.
OL,18,FSpeaking to the media as he arrived at
OL,19,Fcourt, Mr Adams said he was seeking to
OL,20,Fsee the "record corrected".
